data.eml:eml: Three new species of Lebbeus (Crustacea: Decapoda: Hippolytidae) from the Northeastern Pacific

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jensen, Gregory C. (2006): Three new species of Lebbeus (Crustacea: Decapoda: Hippolytidae) from the Northeastern Pacific. Zootaxa 1383: 23-43, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175047
